    <p>We are mov­ing in a very dan­ger­ous di­rec­tion. Our world can­not af­ford a fu­ture where the two largest economies split the globe in a Great Frac­ture – each with its own trade and fi­nan­cial rules and In­ter­net and ar­ti­fi­cial in­tel­li­gence ca­pac­i­ties... We must avoid this at all costs.</p>
    <p>MR AN­TO­NIO GUTER­RES, United Na­tions Sec­re­tary-Gen­eral.</p>

